author: Caitlin Owens
title: Special report: Health care workers vs. coronavirus
description: Health care workers are at an especially high risk of catching the coronavirus, because of their prolonged exposure to patients who have it. Making matters worse, the U.S. doesn't have enough of the protective equipment, like masks and gloves, that keeps them…
